{"pid":"dcfee069096abed49a1bb79dbcb0c8b00785012d","tid":1863221,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:09:55.000Z","msg":"你班仆街落中國行個圈返嚟無事再傾啦"},{"pid":"70540d1777b6c3228fe0c41e26afeabf06f88c30","tid":1863221,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n復赴中國航班咪大流行囉"},{"pid":"c768c651365c0c627479f19913e5ff5dd372ef7f","tid":1863221,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"建議佢自己去視察下先<br />\n咁小事記得唔好戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb51ef5eba954e8d17645bf238f9d1be18bc46e9","tid":1863221,"uid":302360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"Cls組織"},{"pid":"f6c718636cdcd45afb5646575e482bae9b09d625","tid":1863221,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"究竟幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b83757e1232e4e707b2af411cb99222671fad7","tid":1863221,"uid":291947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2e27b8278d31bbf4687f95560592fae37fd796","tid":1863221,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/363/5e39955fdc6a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F363%2F5e39955fdc6a1.jpg&h=c2e348fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世衛組織全球傳染病風險預防部門負責人布里安表示，武<br />\n漢肺炎疫情尚未構成「大流行」。   圖：翻攝YouTube<br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎疫情蔓延20多個國家，世界衛生組織4日仍宣稱，疫情尚未構成「大流行」，本週將與旅遊及觀光業代表進行電話會議，期望能夠恢復飛往中國的航班，甚至呼籲各國能「重新調整」從中國撤僑的政策。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎去年12月出現病例以來，目前中國確診病例衝破2萬例，超過400人喪命，各國紛紛以專機或包機等方式展開撤僑行動，並祭出停發簽證、停航、關閉邊界等措施防止疫情擴散。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，世衛組織（WHO）全球傳染病風險預防部門負責人布里安（Sylvie Briand）4日在瑞士日內瓦表示，雖然湖北省疫情迅速擴散，但目前尚未處於「大流行」，而是處於傳染病的多重病灶階段，中國當局已採取嚴厲措施設法控制疫情，其他受影響的國家也採取行動，以避免病毒進一步擴散。<br />\n<br />\n對於國際間紛紛停航中國一事，布里安表示，機上人員與乘客有相當近距離的接觸，讓他們害怕受到感染，WHO本週將與旅遊及觀光業代表進行電話會議，共同制定保護人員的具體建議，以期能夠恢復飛往中國的航班，「我不能保證，他們會恢復航班。」<br />\n<br />\n她又說，世衛正與各國合作，希望各國有關從中國撤僑的政策能「重新調整」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-02-05/362177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-02-05%2F362177&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=1d1ba4cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-02-05/362177</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"叫隻nigga飛去武汉先啦"},{"pid":"be77bbb92fc348227d189624608de955349a1c24","tid":1863221,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:29:27.000Z","msg":"WHO做乜鳩<br />\n日日出黎奶<br />\n<br />\n人地飛去邊唔飛去邊關你WHO撚事咩"},{"pid":"2b096dc77d283111b9f8185815756be34689b3d8","tid":1863221,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死撚哂啲人先封呀？全球奶哂野先封呀？死 on9！</span>"},{"pid":"340fd91b9cc9d9c5ebf7e233bd141413028f2592","tid":1863221,"uid":71924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，聯合國窮撚到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7801623c0e5d4ade55679513cbf746710ba03a0a","tid":1863221,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"唔睇英文簡寫以為係支共口交部發言.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f86c7faab84d03a761d3bac300096dc114de759","tid":1863221,"uid":28223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"好想知係唔係得連登仔先屌WHO 而家成個口交部咁撚樣"},{"pid":"14fbcb830f4040c9a48812baea09130faf5eee22","tid":1863221,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face